Original Paper
Understanding Experiences of Telehealth in Palliative Care: Photo Interview Study
Mahima Kalla1, BE, PhD; Teresa O'Brien1, BMedSci, PhD; Olivia Metcalf1, PhD; Rashina Hoda2, BSc, PhD; Xiao Chen3, PhD; Andy Li2, BCS, BEngEE (Hons); Catriona Parker4, BAppSc, MAppSc, PhD; Michael Edward Franco2,5,6, MBBS; Sam Georgy7, BSc, BEng, MBA, MSc; Kit Huckvale1, MBChB, BSc, MSc, PhD; Christopher Bain8, MBBS, MInfoTech, PhD; Peter Poon9,10, MBBS, PGDipPM, CHIA
