iera E, Kocaballi B, Halamka J, Laranjo L. The digital scribe. NPJ Digit Med. 2018;1(1):58. [doi: 10.1038/s41746018-0066-9] [Medline: 31304337] 27. Ghatnekar S, Faletsky A, Nambudiri VE. Digital scribe utility and barriers to implementation in clinical practice: a scoping review. Health Technol (Berl). 2021;11(4):803-809. [doi: 10.1007/s12553-021-00568-0] [Medline: 34094806] 28. van Buchem MM, Boosman H, Bauer MP, Kant IMJ, Cammel SA, Steyerberg EW. The digital scribe in clinical practice: a scoping review and research agenda. NPJ Digit Med. Mar 26, 2021;4(1):57. [doi: 10.1038/s41746-021-004325] [Medline: 33772070]
